Angel- (6)
- The angel gains 1 favour each time someone in game respawns, regardless of if the angel is alive or dead.
- The angel can use favours to get weak protection or weak attacks.
- Protecting the Angel themselves costs 1 favour, protecting someone else costs 2 favour. Weak attacking someone costs 3 favour.
- Protection and attacks are both night end and visitng actions. They both have no cooldown, but cannot be each used more than once in 1 night. The angel can only use favours when alive.
- Respawns in 6 phases. 
